  files/emodules.info-gentoo.patch :

  Fixes annoying emodules.info not having a place in the info dir
  (resolves bug #1792).

*xemacs-21.4.6-r2 (15 Apr 2002)

  15 Apr 2002; Matthew Kennedy <mkennedy@gentoo.org>
